QuestData.Title: The Price of Victory
QuestData.Description:
Saurfang... how could this have happened....
<Jaina takes a moment to compose herself.>
The Alliance has known High Overlord Saurfang as both a sworn enemy and an invaluable ally.
Anduin will want to honor his memory. Recall our forces and inform them of what has happened. Genn's soldiers were dispatched to the western gate. You should be able to find him there.
QuestData.LogDescription: Recall the Alliance forces and inform them of what has transpired.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Return to Jaina before the gates of Orgrimmar.
